  "epitaph": "Here lies the Coyote, a ruby-furred ghost,\nWho chased the metadata but froze at the post.\nFifty-eight stars hang dim in the gallery hall,\nFor the API is silent that answered the call.\nThe museum is dark, and the labels are torn,\nA witless project, abandoned and worn.\nRest in /dev/null.",
